  "title": "Business Executive / Assistant (Hybrid Work Arrangement)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Build and maintain good relationships with Charterers.</li>\n  <li>Manage the daily operations of bulk and gas carrier vessels together with the Master and technical team.</li>\n  <li>Serve as the main contact between Technical Managers and Charterers, handling daily communication and problem-solving.</li>\n  <li>Support the Business Manager in research and identifying new business opportunities before chartering.</li>\n  <li>Handle administrative tasks related to contracts and chartering work.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110980</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Lim Hooi Mei</p>",
